Package: herccia
Title: Utilities for creating Civic Infrastructure Assessment reports
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ben", "Taft",
           email = "ben.taft@career2cradle.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Higher Expectations for Racine County", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Perform the data tasks for a StriveTogether Civic Infrastructure
    Assessment. Initially, this package focuses on public data from the US
    Census and Wisconsin's Department of Public Instruction, and internal data
    from Racine Unified School District.
